---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SoftCTA from '../../components/SoftCTA.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — Conduit AI Blog"
  description="Conduit AI Blog focuses on hands-on AI tooling, model selection and cost optimization for individual developers."
  lang="en"
>
  <article class="page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>This blog shares practical ways to use AI tools — tips for Claude Code, Codex and Cursor, how to pick the right model, how to automate workflows, and how to cut costs.</p>
    <p>The rule is simple: <strong>be useful first</strong>. Most of the content is hands-on; the platform only gets a natural mention where it fits.</p>
    <h2>Who it's for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Individual developers and students who want Claude / GPT without overpaying</li>
      <li>People using Claude Code / Cursor / Codex who want to ship faster and spend less</li>
      <li>Anyone weighing which model to use and which billing actually saves money</li>
    </ul>
    <SoftCTA lang="en" />
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.2rem; }
  .page h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .page h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 1.8rem 0 0.6rem; }
  .page p { color: var(--text-soft); }
  .page strong { color: var(--text); }
  .page ul { color: var(--text-soft); padding-left: 1.3rem; }
  .page li { margin: 0.4rem 0; }
</style>
